snippet.title: Intruder Game Play Trailer
snippet.description:
A trailer showing from beginning to end of a match and the aspects of the game. From sneaking through vents to setting up traps for the Intruders. This is a fan-made trailer showcasing this amazing game that has so much potential and what other stealthy games are lacking. More and more content is being added to this game and I can't wait to see what is to come in the future!

Visit their site where you can buy it! Along with their YouTube Channel which posts updates and more!
https://superbossgames.com/intruder/ 
https://www.youtube.com/user/SuperbossGames
Thank you Rob and Austin for this amazing game!



P.S. Rob sorry it took so long for me to upload this ( over a year ) college got in the way. - Mikeyy
